the Model T, it took
13 hours to assemble.

7
00:02:02,392 --> 00:02:06,422
Within five years,
he was turning out
a vehicle every 90 seconds.

8
00:02:09,543 --> 00:02:12,062
Of course, the real invention
wasn't the car,

9
00:02:12,144 --> 00:02:14,503
it was the assembly line
that built it.

10
00:02:16,483 --> 00:02:20,413
Pretty soon, other businesses
had borrowed
the same techniques.

11
00:02:21,184 --> 00:02:24,273
Seamstresses
became button sewers.

12
00:02:24,354 --> 00:02:27,323
Furniture makers
became knob turners.

13
00:02:28,655 --> 00:02:32,025
lt was the beginning
and the end of imagination

14
00:02:32,095 --> 00:02:34,424
all at the same time.

15
