that would grow over time.

116
00:13:57,744 --> 00:14:02,374
The real effect of
October 29th took
a little longer to sink in.

117
00:14:06,215 --> 00:14:10,204
By noon, all the gains
of the previous year
had been obliterated.

118
00:14:11,826 --> 00:14:16,316
By 4:00 p.m.,
nearly $10 billion
of market value was gone.

119
00:14:19,696 --> 00:14:22,896
