Displaced families
took to the American highway

123
00:14:44,428 --> 00:14:47,358
in the last possession
that remained to them,

124
00:14:47,828 --> 00:14:49,458
their automobile.

125
00:14:52,229 --> 00:14:55,638
And all at once,
millions of Americans

126
